11 March 2010Minister of Public Enterprise, Barbara Hogan and Minster of Energy, Dipuo Peters will brief members of the media on Eskom s loan application from the World Bank.The briefing will take place as follows:Date: Friday, 12 March 2010 Time: 10h30 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNote: There will be a linkup to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape TownEnquiries:Bongiwe Gambu 082 714 9463Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)